text: Maia McCall Mitchell (born 18 August 1993) is an Australian actress and singer. She is known for her roles as Brittany Flune in the children's television series Mortified, and as Natasha Ham in the teen drama Trapped. Mitchell starred in the drama The Fosters as Callie Adams Foster.
